[The number of cases has risen to 38 with one death. At a county fair, the 2 most likely sources for the pathogen are a petting zoo (there were 5) or a food source. We await additional information about this outbreak of EHEC.

The state of North Carolina can be located on the HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map at http://healthmap.org/r/3Hk_. The counties mentioned can be seen on the map at http://www.digital-topo-maps.com/county-map/north-carolina.shtml. The state of South Carolina can be seen on an interactive map at http://healthmap.org/r/1AYi. - Mod.LL]
